Package edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.processing

Annotation Type ParameterDescription

@Documented
@Target(TYPE)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface ParameterDescription
A description of processor parameters.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements
    Modifier and Type Required Element Description
    java.lang.String name
    The parameter name / key.

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    java.lang.String dataType
    The expected data type of the parameter.

    Whether the parameter is required, i.e.

  • Element Details

    • name

      java.lang.String name
      The parameter name / key.
      Returns:
      String name / key for the parameter.

    • description

      java.lang.String description
      A short description of the parameter and what it does.
      Returns:
      String description of the parameter.
      Default:
      ""

    • dataType

      java.lang.String dataType
      The expected data type of the parameter.
      Returns:
      String expected data; str, float, or bool; List[T] or Mapping[T1, T2] of those.
      Default:
      ""

    • required

      boolean required
      Whether the parameter is required, i.e. needed by the processor in order to function.
      Returns:
      True if parameter is required, False if not required.
      Default:
      false
